<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-4035] AclCommand should allow Describe operation on groups</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4035</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, AclCommand stores the following mapping in ResourceTypeToValidOperations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Group -&amp;gt; Set(Read, All)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This prevents users from setting a Describe operation on a consumer group, which is a valid combination. We should add Describe to the set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
